00:05:08.779 --> 00:05:17.620
But now, what is the second thing we can do to cause someone to stumble, placing an obstacle

00:05:17.620 --> 00:05:19.019
in their path?

00:05:19.180 --> 00:05:23.259
Again, this is true physically or spiritually.

00:05:23.259 --> 00:05:29.019
And if you think about it, whether we put that stumbling block there intentionally or

00:05:29.019 --> 00:05:32.579
unintentionally, the results is the same, isn't?

