As mentioned in today's Watchtower comments, wholesome speech and upright conduct can help

00:05:38.420 --> 00:05:42.819
us to avoid ever being a cause for stumbling.

00:05:42.819 --> 00:05:45.819
In contrast, unwholesome speech.

00:05:45.819 --> 00:05:51.180
Stumbling conduct can easily stumble ones inside or outside the congregation.

