00:07:13.860 --> 00:07:16.500
We could call this a sin of omission.

00:07:16.500 --> 00:07:19.980
And again, it applies physically and spiritually.

00:07:19.980 --> 00:07:25.339
As a physical example, let's say we see the floor has just been mocked.

