00:08:35.580 --> 00:08:37.940
trip hazard.

00:08:37.940 --> 00:08:44.139
Rather than being any cause for stumbling, we want to be a force for good, don't we?

00:08:44.139 --> 00:08:49.460
Helping others to stand firm and even helping ones get up if they have fallen.
